{"tid":223528,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【電競狂熱．有片】15靚女熱血追電競夢　豪言：女仔打機唔一定廢","createTime":"2017-04-30T11:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:05:05.000Z","uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bdf55decf7ef5546f10372827156a20d482dc280","tid":223528,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"打機會令人沉迷已經是過時的偏見，近年電子競技為不少國家賺錢，韓國更將電競發展成為「國技」，訓練選手參與比賽成為「職業運動員」。但不論外國或本港，女子電競賽仍屬小數，電競公司舉辦女子限定的「女王盃」《英雄聯盟》電競賽，今日(15日)進行決賽，三隊脫穎而出的隊伍，合共15名女選手，平均只有20歲，她們毫不留力，只為展示爭取成為職業選手的決心，更希望推翻「女仔打機廢」的成見，有選手立下宣言：「女仔並唔係花瓶，同其他男仔一樣做到的。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21jjLtCjsAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D21jjLtCjsAc&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=08886e6e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21jjLtCjsAc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/524037/xlarge/12d286330e1b5b375021d0c0db638e75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F524037%2Fxlarge%2F12d286330e1b5b375021d0c0db638e75.jpg&h=405e1178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女子電競比賽時戰況亦為激烈，團員不時高談戰術望能盡快打對手擊退。（梁煥敏攝）<br />\n三隊進入最後決賽的女子隊伍包括有Miss Rippers、Kira Zenith及Team Dream Force，其中順利打入冠軍賽的Team Dream Force（TDF）成軍4個月，平均打了《英雄聯盟》4至5年，各人不約而同表示希望成為職業電競選手，並以《英雄聯盟》作契機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/524042/xlarge/c24aa1ea19753a526df74ec517e02cb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F524042%2Fxlarge%2Fc24aa1ea19753a526df74ec517e02cb6.jpg&h=f8d4ebf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n選手之一，應屆DSE考生Juicy（前左）望能得到家人體諒，支持她成為職業電競手。（梁煥敏攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n團員為「追夢」努力練習，每人每日至少練習8小時，亦不時進行團練，每次最少打5場。團員之一「Bridyyy」（上圖前右）表示與男士組隊往往只能作支援角色，但她非常不認同，「好多人覺得女仔打機只係花瓶，但我哋想用實力證明」。<br />\n電競手坦言難以得到家人認同<br />\n<br />\n團員Sweety（上圖後右）表示，家人其實不太認同自己以打機作職業，對「電競」存有偏見，坦言只有一年時間給自己追夢，「一年內做唔到成績就要搵工，被逼放棄夢想」。隊員Juicy為今屆DSE考生，她指自己分配時間，上午溫書，其後有時間才進行練習。希望成為職業選手的她現時仍游說父母，望他們能認同自己所想。「佢哋見到我有得去比賽，又俾人訪問會覺得開心，都會認同我嘅！」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/84657/-%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E7%8B%82%E7%86%B1-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-15%E9%9D%9A%E5%A5%B3%E7%86%B1%E8%A1%80%E8%BF%BD%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%A4%A2-%E8%B1%AA%E8%A8%80-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%94%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E5%94%94%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F84657%2F-%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E7%258B%2582%25E7%2586%25B1-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-15%25E9%259D%259A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A1%2580%25E8%25BF%25BD%25E9%259B%25BB%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E5%25A4%25A2-%25E8%25B1%25AA%25E8%25A8%2580-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%2589%2593%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%2594%2594%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BB%25A2&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusrwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=620a8836\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/84657/-%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E7%8B%82%E7%86%B1-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-15%E9%9D%9A%E5%A5%B3%E7%86%B1%E8%A1%80%E8%BF%BD%E9%9B%BB%E7%AB%B6%E5%A4%A2-%E8%B1%AA%E8%A8%80-%E5%A5%B3%E4%BB%94%E6%89%93%E6%A9%9F%E5%94%94%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%9A%E5%BB%A2</a>"},{"pid":"7a42f9bcaab696b1c56d708a5391d512af26b000","tid":223528,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6871543029d2edcbc1c79f2482833790e9298bc1","tid":223528,"uid":73227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"屌又post old news"},{"pid":"156bef8ad7cff5a310f7c51e10ea1849144fc4df","tid":223528,"uid":68084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:47:55.000Z","msg":"靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n全部都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> wo"},{"pid":"56d9f95fb498789d49518aa1e0a34e3426dd9ba